long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: "Open in Discord" is a lightweight and efficient Chrome extension designed to enhance your experience with Discord links on the web. It seamlessly redirects Discord channel links to open directly in the Discord desktop application, providing a more integrated and convenient user experience for Discord users.
